<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Home | Aaron Taylor Hammer</title>
  <% include ../partials/scripts %>
  <% include ../partials/style %>
</head>

<body>


  <% include ../partials/header %>
  <div class="main">
    <div id="main-content">
      <h1>About:</h1>
      <h3>
        This page is fully autogenerated and the values are updated each page refresh (until coinigy has better websocket docs). Eventually I want to show
        daily, weekly, monthly, yearly, and all time returns but this will be diffucult as I can pull and add funds and I'm held back by coinigy's API.
        I also wish to make it a bit more a e s t h e t i c and possibly attempt to tell when a trade made and lost money and coloring them red/green by that.
      <h3>
      <h3>
        Please note this is crypto currency trading only not stocks.
      <h3>

      <h1>Current Crypto Balance: $<%= totalBalanceEJS %></h1>
      <h4> Crypto abbreviation | Amount owned | USD worth </h4>
      <% for(var i = 0; i < cryptoDataEJS.length; i++) {%>
        <br>
        <br>
        <% for(var j = 0; j < cryptoDataEJS[i].length; j++) {%>
          <b style="font-size: 150%;"><%= cryptoDataEJS[i][j] %> |</b>
        <% } %>
      <% } %>

      <br>
      <br>
      <br>
      <h1>Recent Trades</h1>
      <h4> What was Traded | Buy or Sell | Type of Trade | Amount | Date </h4>
      <% for(var i = 0; i < orderDataEJS.length; i++) {%>
        <br>
        <% for(var j = 0; j < orderDataEJS[i].length; j++) {%>
          <b style="font-size: 150%;"><%= orderDataEJS[i][j] %> |</b>
        <% } %>
      <% } %>
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />



        <h1>Current Securities/Cash Balance: $<%= accountTotalValueEJS %></h1>
        <h2>Current Securities Balance: $<%= accountSecuritiesValueEJS %></h2>
        <h2>Current Cash Balance: $<%= accountCashValueEJS %></h2>
        <h4> Crypto abbreviation | Amount owned | USD worth </h4>
        <% for(var i = 0; i < stockHoldingsEJS.length; i++) {%>
          <br>
          <br>
          <% for(var j = 0; j < stockHoldingsEJS[i].length; j++) {%>
            <b style="font-size: 150%;"><%= stockHoldingsEJS[i][j] %> |</b>
          <% } %>
        <% } %>




    </div>

  </div>


  <% include ../partials/footer %>
</body>

</html>
